These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-1::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, corn, grapefruit, potato
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, singing, chess, video-games
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, surfing, badminton, skateboarding
 1. the person who's hobby is chess is in an odd position##4
 2. the person eating potato is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 3. the person who's sport is badminton is not to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##8
 4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is not the person eating potato##6
 5. the person eating grapefruit is somewhere to the right of the person eating carrot##5
 6. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 7. the person who's sport is badminton is not to the left of the person eating corn##8
 8. the person eating corn is not the person who's sport is skateboarding##6
 9. the person eating carrot is not the person who's hobby is video-games##6
10. the person who's sport is surfing is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
11. the person eating corn is not to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##8
12. the person eating corn is in an even position##4
13. the person eating potato is not to the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##8
14. the person who's hobby is chess is not to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Food    | carrot         | potato     | grapefruit     | corn         |
| Hobby   | singing | video-games    | chess     | drawing |
| Sport   | snowboarding       | surfing | skateboarding | badminton       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, mirinda, soy-milk, fanta
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, fisherman, project-manager, chef
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, soccer, cycling, skiing
 1. the project-manager is not to the right of the chef##8
 2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left##1
 3. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 4. the person drinking fanta is the fisherman##1
 5. the designer is not the person drinking soy-milk##6
 6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 7. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the designer##1
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 9. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the project-manager##5
10. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | soy-milk          | almond-milk      | fanta      | mirinda   |
| Job        | project-manager     | designer | fisherman | chef      |
| Sport      | skiing | soccer    | parkour  | cycling |

