.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, traveling, singing, rock-climbing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, jazz, rock, electronic
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, motorbike, scooter, ship
 1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 2. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the scooter##5
 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 4. the fan of jazz is somewhere to the left of the person driving the ship##5
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is not the fan of dubstep##6
 6. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 7. the fan of dubstep is not to the right of the fan of electronic##8
 8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the fan of rock##1
 9. the person who's hobby is traveling is in an even position##4
10. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the left of the person driving the motorbike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | singing  | traveling | rock-climbing | hiking |
| Music-Genre   | jazz  | dubstep      | electronic | rock        |
| Transport     | quad-bike | scooter       | ship    | motorbike     |

