.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, musical, martial-arts, epic
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, blues, house, techno
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, british, italian, french
 1. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the fan of techno##1
 2. the british is not to the left of the fan of blues##8
 3. the fan of techno is somewhere to the right of the person watching animation movies##5
 4. the person watching animation movies is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching musical movies is not to the right of the british##8
 6. the italian is not to the right of the person watching epic movies##8
 7. the fan of house is somewhere to the left of the person watching epic movies##5
 8. the french is somewhere to the right of the british##5
 9. the egyptian is on the left of the italian##1
10. the person watching epic movies is the italian##1
11. the fan of ambient is somewhere to the right of the fan of blues##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | animation   | epic | musical    | martial-arts |
| Music-Genre   | house    | blues     | ambient   | techno     |
| Nationality   | egyptian | italian   | british | french    |

