.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, skydiving, baking, camping
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, crime, family, martial-arts
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, golf, surfing, skiing
 1. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is golf##5
 2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
 3. the person watching comedy movies is on the far right##1
 4. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is baking##5
 5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 6. the person watching martial-arts movies is not the person who's hobby is baking##6
 7. the person who's hobby is singing is not the person who's sport is surfing##6
 8. the person watching crime movies is the person who's sport is surfing##1
 9. the person watching family movies is not to the right of the person who's hobby is singing##8
10. the person who's sport is skiing is the person who's hobby is baking##1
11. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the left of the person watching family movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby         | baking       | singing | skydiving  | camping    |
| Movie-Genre   | family       | martial-arts    | crime | comedy    |
| Sport         | skiing | cycling   | surfing   | golf |

