.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-6::.
There 4 different types of food: onion, banana, cucumber, corn
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, western, family, satire
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, australian, turkish, argentine
 1. the person eating cucumber is not to the left of the person watching spy movies##8
 2. the person watching satire movies is not the australian##6
 3. the turkish is somewhere between the person eating banana and the person watching satire movies##7
 4. the australian is not to the left of the person watching western movies##8
 5. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the person eating corn##3
 6. the turkish is the person watching spy movies##1
 7. the person eating onion is somewhere to the right of the person watching family movies##5
 8. the argentine is between the person eating onion and the turkish##2
 9. the person watching satire movies is not to the right of the person eating onion##8
10. the person eating cucumber is not to the right of the person eating corn##8
11. the japanese is somewhere to the left of the person watching satire movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Food          | banana      | cucumber      | corn | onion |
| Movie-Genre   | family | spy    | satire | western     |
| Nationality   | japanese    | turkish | argentine  | australian |

