There 4 different types of food: peach, radish, apricot, eggplant
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, indie, salsa, folk
1. the person eating apricot is somewhere to the right of the person eating eggplant##5
2. the person eating peach is somewhere between the person eating eggplant and the person eating apricot##7
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
4. the fan of salsa is not to the right of the person drinking milk##8
5. the person eating eggplant is somewhere to the right of the person drinking 7up##5
6. the person eating peach is not to the right of the person drinking mirinda##8
7. the person eating eggplant is the fan of indie##1
8. the person eating eggplant is somewhere between the fan of folk and the person drinking 7up##7
9. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |     3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | 7up     | hot-chocolate | mirinda  | milk |
| Food          | radish | eggplant   | peach | apricot |
| Music-Genre   | metal     | indie   | folk      | salsa      |

