 1. the person who's hobby is camping is not to the right of the person driving the bike##8
 2. the canadian is somewhere between the person driving the boat and the nigerian##7
 3. the person who's hobby is collecting is not to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##8
 4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the indian is not to the left of the person who's hobby is camping##8
 7. the canadian is on the left or right of the indian##3
 8. the indian is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##5
 9. the person who's hobby is collecting is not to the left of the person driving the bike##8
10. the person driving the trike is not to the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##8
11. the indian is not to the left of the person who's hobby is singing##8
12. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
13. the indian is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##5
14. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |      3      |     4      |
| Hobby         | puzzles    | camping | singing | collecting    |
| Nationality   | nigerian  | canadian    | indian      | french |
| Transport     | quad-bike | bike          | boat      | trike       |

