.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, fanta, hot-chocolate, water
The people have 4 different jobs:  musician, journalist, teacher, freelancer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, scientific, musical, horror
 1. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the person watching sports movies##5
 2. the teacher is not the person drinking sprite##6
 3. the freelancer is the person drinking fanta##1
 4. the teacher is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
 5. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the musician##3
 6. the person watching musical movies is the teacher##1
 7. the journalist is not to the right of the teacher##8
 8. the teacher is not to the left of the person drinking water##8
 9. the teacher is somewhere to the left of the person watching scientific movies##5
10. the teacher is somewhere to the right of the journalist##5
11. the musician is not the person drinking fanta##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2   |    3     |      4      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate     | water  | fanta | sprite |
| Job           | journalist | teacher | freelancer | musician   |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | musical  | scientific   | sports   |

