 4. the person eating eggplant is not to the left of the person eating spinach##8
 5. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##5
 6. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is reading##5
 7. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 8. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
 9. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3
10. the person eating cauliflower is not to the right of the person who's hobby is singing##8
11. the person eating eggplant is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2      |     3      |     4     |
