 6. the lawyer is on the right of the dancer##1
 7. the freelancer is the person driving the skateboard##1
 8. the person driving the bus is not the social-worker##6
 9. the freelancer is not to the left of the spanish##8
10. the spanish is not to the right of the social-worker##8
