 4. the person watching musical movies is between the person driving the ship and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
 5. the person driving the ship is not to the right of the person watching thriller movies##8
 6. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3
 7. the person driving the ship is not to the left of the person driving the airplane##8
 8. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 9. the person watching horror movies is not to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##8
10. the person driving the airplane is not to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##8
11. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching romance movies##5
12. the person driving the train is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
13. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
