6. the colombian is between the owner of the snake and the person who's sport is cycling##2
7. the colombian is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is golf##5
8. the polish is not to the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##8
9. the colombian is on the right of the malaysian##1

