.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, american, nigerian, indian
4 different pets are kept: rat, goldfish, turtle, bird
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, volleyball, ice-hockey, cricket
1. the owner of the rat is the person who's sport is cycling##1
2. the american is not to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##8
3. the person who's sport is cricket is between the owner of the rat and the owner of the bird##2
4. the argentine is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the american is not the person who's sport is ice-hockey##6
6. the owner of the bird is on the left of the indian##1
7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere between the person who's sport is cricket and the person who's sport is volleyball##7
8. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
9. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | american | argentine     | indian  | nigerian |
| Pet           | goldfish      | bird        | turtle   | rat |
| Sport         | volleyball  | ice-hockey | cricket | cycling       |

 